#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/flash.rst:144
#: d3e136873ec94eef94ae5a61bff8bce6
msgid "WB2模块外置FLASH和内置FLASH有什么区别"
msgstr ""
"What is the difference between external Flash and internal Flash of the WB2 "
"module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/flash.rst:145
#: 6763970673034743b00250aed354c029
msgid ""
"模块外置FLASH指的是模组内部除了有一个WIFI芯片还带有一个flash芯片；模块内置"
"flash指的是WIFI芯片自带flash"
msgstr ""
"External FLASH of the module means that, in addition to a Wi-Fi chip, there "
"is also a Flash chip inside the module; internal Flash of the module means "
"that the Wi-Fi chip comes with built-in Flash."
